                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "In Foul Legacy Transformation, Beidou is a formidable character that can unleash Electro DMG off-field and reliably trigger Electro-Charged (NOTE: This weapon's special effect does NOT buff Electro-Charged). While Electro-Charged, Beidou can unleash Hydro and Electro DMG simultaneously, thereby fully utilizing this weapon's special effect. Therefore, this weapon is an ideal choice for her.",
